\section{Entry vectors}

The file loads at [[$0800]] and is entered at its first byte by the
library's \textsc{brun}. The second vector replays the animation
without re-running \texttt{MAKE.INDATA} (the attract loop uses it),
and the third is a no-op hook.

<<u1intro entry vectors>>=
        ORG $0800
INTRO_ENTRY
        JMP INTRO_COLD
INTRO_REPLAY_VEC
        JMP INTRO_REPLAY
        RTS                             ; spare no-op vector
@ %def INTRO_ENTRY INTRO_REPLAY_VEC

